{
  "message": "test(random): add Generator consistency differential cases across seed/bound/prefix boundaries\n\nAdded 10 goldens covering DeterministicRng boundary conditions that\nwere thin in the differential suite:\n\n- next_f64_unit_interval: seed=0 (1024 draws), near-u64::MAX seed\n  (512 draws) \u2014 exercises the [0,1) range contract at seed extremes\n- bounded_u64_grid: prime bound 1048573, power-of-two bound 65536,\n  u64::MAX-1 bound \u2014 catches modulo-bias drift at non-power-of-two\n  and near-max bounds\n- same_seed_stream: zero-seed 4096 draws\n- different_seed_diverges: adjacent seeds (7000 vs 7001) within\n  128 draws \u2014 low-Hamming-distance seeds must still decorrelate\n- jump_ahead_equivalence: 10000-step jump\n- state_restore_replay: zero-prefix (fresh state restore) and\n  8192-prefix (large prior advancement)\n\n36 rng_differential cases total (from 26).\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
